<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/schemes/side> rdf:type owl:Ontology ;
                                     dc:creator "Airy Magnien" ;
                                     dc:description "List of terms denoting the faces and sides of, typically, a box-like solid" ;
                                     dc:title "Sides terminology"@en ;
                                     vann:preferredNamespacePrefix "side" ;
                                     vann:preferredNamespaceUri "https://cdm.ovh/rsm/schemes/side" ;
                                     dcterms:created "2 April 2024" ;
                                     dcterms:license "https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" ;
                                     rdfs:comment "designation of faces (left, right...) can be used in conjunction with the side of the faces (interior, exterior). Again, orientation and polarity shall be disambiguated by the context in which they are expressed."@en ;
                                     skos:scopeNote "Scheme of principal side designations relative to an intrinsic or contextual reference frame. Applicability depends on the geometry, function, or orientation of the entity concerned. The usage context should provide all necessary disambiguation."@en .

